@PeterSweden7 Why risk importing criminals, hoping to find some "good apples"? 

Why sacrifice *some* of your women and children for the sake of "diversity"? 

Sacrificing safety for "diversity" isn’t kindness, it’s reckless betrayal and cruelty to your constituents! #massdeportation

Is there a particular reason why you left out #MassDeportation sangha ?

